title: New Creator: Kellen Smalley
body:
New member: Kellen Smalley
Social handle: https://cle.go.twitch.tv/smalldogg
Community Treasury grant tier: $0
Info: Kellen is a core team member of Rally and works closely with creators.  Given the recent discussion and proposals around liquidity pools, Kellen will be an instrumental part of the registry in putting forth these types of economic proposals.
